Package mph.gui

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ComparableDeliverable
    Class used in the GUI, to sort a list of deliverables by deadline date.
    It implements Comparable.
    FolderNode
    Class used to display a folder icon for professor and course nodes in the JTree even if they haven't got children.
    It extends DefaultMutableTreeNode.
    LoginScreen
    This GUI class lets a user log into the MPH system.
    It extends JFrame.
    TreeCourse
    Used to print a short name for the courses displayed in the JTree.
    It extends TreeEntity.
    TreeEntity
    Abstract class used to print a 'nice' name for the entities displayed in the JTree.
    TreeProfessor
    Used to print a short name for the professors displayed in the JTree.
    It extends TreeEntity.
    TreeProject
    Used to print a short name for the projects displayed in the JTree.
    It extends TreeEntity.
